(Body/card improvements) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(Problem) Tj
T*
(- Several cards used fixed heights and strict minimum widths.) Tj
T*
(- On smaller devices this can create cramped content, uneven spacing, and overflow.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(Fix) Tj
T*
(- Standardized card sizing with responsive flex values.) Tj
T*
(- On mobile \(max-width: 768px\), switched major cards to height: auto so content defines the height.) Tj
T*
(- Relaxed strict min-width behavior at smaller breakpoints.) Tj
T*
(- Adjusted text/image sizing and spacing for smaller screens.) Tj
T*
(- Improved stacking for intro section and list sections.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(Why it works) Tj
T*
(Responsive layouts should prioritize fluid sizing. height: auto on mobile avoids clipping, and small) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(3\) Adding a simple fade-in on page load) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(Problem) Tj
T*
(The page appeared instantly without transition.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(Fix) Tj
T*
(- Added a keyframe animation to the body:) Tj
T*
(  - starts at opacity: 0) Tj
T*
(  - ends at opacity: 1) Tj
T*
(  - duration: 0.7s) Tj
T*
(- Added reduced-motion support:) Tj
T*
(  - @media \(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce\) disables animation and transitions.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(Why it works) Tj
T*
(Fade-in adds a gentle first impression. Reduced-motion support keeps the experience accessible for u) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
